To you, General Affairs Manager.

6
00:01:27,523 --> 00:01:31,891
I don't ask about the business status of our Asia Processing Company

7
00:01:32,859 --> 00:01:34,156
The president, we are

8
00:01:34,654 --> 00:01:40,654
