18
00:02:09,889 --> 00:02:11,904
Three heads of sales management

19
00:02:12,224 --> 00:02:14,037
Looks like there are 16 Chiefs in our division

20
00:02:15,428 --> 00:02:16,334
So 19 people in total?

21
00:02:16,359 --> 00:02:17,756
The restructuring has begun

22
00:02:17,795 --> 00:02:19,224
Will we ordinary employees also be restructured?

23
00:02:19,326 --> 00:02:20,435
I think so

24
00:02:21,162 --> 00:02:25,834
Those who want to get ahead through the power of academic cliques should be careful

25
00:02:27,709 --> 00:02:30,896
It seems that all the department heads that were called in graduate from S university

26
00:02:31,256 --> 00:02:34,787
It means These are the former president's henchmen

27
00:02:35,170 --> 00:02:36,826
Speaking of S university,our Chief also graduated from S university,right?

28
00:02:36,967 --> 00:02:37,771
Yes he is

29
00:02:37,982 --> 00:02:42,670
so After five years with the company, he surpassed Mr. Ishida, who was two years his senior, to become a section chief

30
00:03:04,951 --> 00:03:05,560
See you

31
00:03:05,662 --> 00:03:06,482
Good night

32
00:03:10,209 --> 00:03:11,474
Welcome to our store

33
00:03:13,474 --> 00:03:16,271
I'm sorry I'm late

34
00:03:16,646 --> 00:03:17,592
Can you pass me the hand towel?

35
00:03:17,617 --> 00:03:18,146
Yes

36
00:03:18,209 --> 00:03:20,209
I'm starving

37
00:03:20,662 --> 00:03:21,873
Oh, You're just drinking?

38
00:03:22,709 --> 00:03:23,615
Shall we eat something?

39
00:03:24,295 --> 00:03:25,748
May I help you?

40
00:03:26,592 --> 00:03:28,286
One serving of pork cutlet, please

41
00:03:28,325 --> 00:03:28,810
Yes

42
00:03:29,076 --> 00:03:29,639
One beer

43
00:03:29,756 --> 00:03:30,178
Yes

44
00:03:32,131 --> 00:03:33,920
You don't drink anything but beers

45
00:03:36,857 --> 00:03:38,240
Did you have a bad day at the office?

46
00:03:38,381 --> 00:03:40,701
What happen if I resign from the company ?

47
00:03:41,099 --> 00:03:44,396
I have never thought about that

48
00:03:45,201 --> 00:03:46,545
I don't want to be a husband with no economic power

49
00:03:46,740 --> 00:03:48,592
What are you talking about?

50
00:03:49,326 --> 00:03:51,389
Oh I just remembered, Excuse me

51
00:03:51,764 --> 00:03:53,553
I'll have a pork cutlet sandwich to go, please

52
00:03:56,381 --> 00:03:58,857
You have not eaten the pork cutlet sandwich yet

53
00:04:00,068 --> 00:04:01,506
You can eat it

54
00:04:05,717 --> 00:04:07,420
You have not had a dinner yet,right?

55
00:04:10,357 --> 00:04:11,771
What's wrong with you?

56
00:04:13,662 --> 00:04:14,943
It's bad you drink a lot

57
00:04:16,068 --> 00:04:17,592
Here it is.
This is Yummy

58
00:04:17,717 --> 00:04:18,849
I don't feel like eating

59
00:04:20,881 --> 00:04:24,451
I think you has something wrong at company

60
00:04:25,099 --> 00:04:27,482
Please tell me

61
00:04:27,967 --> 00:04:29,318
Nothing wrong

62
00:04:29,748 --> 00:04:32,592
You just told me you resign from the company or something..

63
00:04:32,724 --> 00:04:35,389
You are too noisy.
I've told you nothing wrong!

64
00:04:38,740 --> 00:04:40,021
I'm sorry

65
00:04:41,170 --> 00:04:42,881
I won't ask you anything

66
00:04:43,943 --> 00:04:47,951
But We promised not to hide things from each other

67
00:04:48,756 --> 00:04:50,974
Please keep the promise

68
00:04:56,646 --> 00:04:59,326
Sorry... I'm something wrong today

69
00:05:00,670 --> 00:05:02,498
Oh..It's too late so I have to leave now

70
00:05:03,029 --> 00:05:04,357
There's still the last train

71
00:05:04,396 --> 00:05:04,857
Yes

72
00:05:06,192 --> 00:05:07,614
You should take a rest too

73
00:05:07,646 --> 00:05:08,005
Um

74
00:05:08,474 --> 00:05:09,818
Be careful of having a cold

75
00:05:09,912 --> 00:05:10,240
I know

76
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:19,146
A total of 84 people at the head office and plants are being restructured

77
00:05:19,466 --> 00:05:21,232
84 people is 40% of the total factory.

78
00:05:21,841 --> 00:05:23,373
Next, it's the employees' turn

79
00:05:23,724 --> 00:05:25,623
