80
00:05:26,044 --> 00:05:28,654
It's just an employment union.
It won't work

81
00:05:29,754 --> 00:05:31,645
By the way,What will happen to chief’s company housing?

82
00:05:32,871 --> 00:05:35,308
They said they'd sell it to him for 70% of the market value.

83
00:05:35,333 --> 00:05:36,809
He can't afford to double his severance pay

84
00:05:36,863 --> 00:05:38,035
That's too bad

85
00:05:38,254 --> 00:05:39,848
They told him if he didn't like it, he should get out of his house.

86
00:05:40,168 --> 00:05:41,238
That's ridiculous

87
00:05:41,332 --> 00:05:42,840
This is the fate of businessmen

88
00:05:44,051 --> 00:05:45,957
Today you, tomorrow me

89
00:05:46,809 --> 00:05:48,176
Chief,There is a visitor

90
00:05:48,348 --> 00:05:48,981
Thank you

91
00:05:50,059 --> 00:05:51,652
Shinpei Miyagawa

92
00:05:53,535 --> 00:05:53,965
Please take one

93
00:05:54,168 --> 00:05:54,645
Thank you

